SHUTDOWN(8)            System Manager's Manual           SHUTDOWN(8)

NAME
       shutdown - shut down system/emulator

SYNOPSIS
       shutdown -h

       shutdown -r

DESCRIPTION
       Shutdown  halts (-h) or restarts (-r) emu(1) or a native ker‚Äê
       nel.  If restarted, emu(1) will be given the same options  as
       were given it when it started.

FILES
       /dev/sysctl

SOURCE
       /dis/shutdown
              sh(1) script

SEE ALSO
       cons(3)

